videos.headline: UNLV jumps ahead with 41-yard TD run
videos.description: UNLV RB Evan Owens breaks a tackle and charges up the sideline to give UNLV a 7-6 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UNLV jumps ahead with 41-yard TD run) 2018/09/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Arkansas State reclaims lead with 24-yard TD pass
videos.description: QB Justice Hansen throws a strike to Jonathan Adams Jr., who makes a diving catch in the end zone and makes it 13-7 Red Wolves.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Arkansas State reclaims lead with 24-yard TD pass) 2018/09/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: UNLV goes back in front on 10-yard TD run
videos.description: RB Lexington Thomas bursts to the outside and finds the end zone to make it 20-19 Rebels.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UNLV goes back in front on 10-yard TD run) 2018/09/22 ESHEET
